This folder should contain the following 3 files:
ca.der
cert.der
private.der

Download AmazonRootCA1.pem from 
https://www.amazontrust.com/repository/AmazonRootCA1.pem

The files are downloaded from AWS IoT
<id>-certificate.pem.crt
<id>-private.pem.key

Commands to convert cert to DER-format:
$ openssl x509 -in mything-certificate.pem.crt -out cert.der -outform DER
$ openssl rsa -in mything-private.pem.key -out private.der -outform DER
$ openssl x509 -in AmazonRootCA1.pem -out ca.der -outform DER
